NAME
	rotd - Report of the day

DESCRIPTION
	rotd generates a daily PDF with information of
	your choosing. It may contain, for example,
	birthday reminders, upcoming events, today's
	schedule, and whether reports.

	The idea, is to have cron run its every morning,
	before you wake up, and either print out the
	PDF, e-mail it do you, or store it on your
	home or desktop directory, or anything else you
	can imagine.
